<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span><span class="c2">(فَأَغْوَيْنَاكُمْ إِنَّا كُنَّا غَاوِينَ (٣٢)</span><a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
